    "jei.havenede.mechanical_hammers.desc.line": "The Mechanical Hammer is a machine that, when supplied with Forge Energy (FE), will hammer blocks without a player having to do it themselves. It can operate without a hammer, but adding any hammer will double the speed, and efficiency enchantments on the hammer will further increase speed. It also supports three different modes of redstone control. Since Ex Deorum does not provide a way to generate FE, you will need another mod to provide power.",
